E mèrè World Climate Change Conference na Moscow site n'ubochi irí abụọ na itoolu n'ọnwa Septemba ruo ụbọchị atọ n'ọnwa Ọktoba, 2003
Ọ bụ Vladimir Putin, onye isi ala nkè Russian Federation, butere ụzọ ịkpọkọta Nzukọ ahụ
Nzukọ ahụ bụ nke Russian Federation kpọrọ, ma kwado ya site na ndị otu mba ụwa gụnyere United Nations
E kwesịghị ịgbagwoju ya anya na World Climate Conferences.
